Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OP ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}绚烂夺目 不堪直视
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的冲动 因为你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窥探 想知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真实的心请允许我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}数着星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你与我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儿时仰望天际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔诚祈祷的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿与你携手去往无限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成为导航未来之光
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part A ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,巨兽南下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,胡闹什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 拉莱雅到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,注意礼仪 这里可是别人家的军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈还没跟古匈总监提那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…一直没顾上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想请Megafauna驶往Capital特区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有这种想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有来自宇宙的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想Capital军和亚美利亚必须联合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和它进行对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想法确实不错 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果宇宙脐带教的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,愿意就「来自宇宙的威胁」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,向我们进行说明 那自然好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,起码就我个人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,从未听法皇大人提起过这些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 为了交接光子电池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙脐带教会定期派人登上圣波尔图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还有荷米斯玫瑰设计图的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,多尼尔舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,用米诺夫斯基低空飞行…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不成问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那样可吃电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦登上大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以找到有线电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,通过它 我能叫来帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或是领路或是保驾护航
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,180度转向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,通知全员 检查货物固定情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定航线 宜候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:59.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}宜候：日本幕府海军时期航海用语，宜しく候（よろしくそうろう）的简化。\N{\alpha&HFF&}宜候：{\alpha}原意是笔直前进，后作为复述命令时的用语，表示「明白」「一切正常」。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero没驾驶员驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会太暴殄天物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？没人开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋研究所又不是驾校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,送克里姆中尉的Armorzagan不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们去时就做好了当诱饵的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,米克的Armorzagan摆脱了敌人的拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉这时回国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是总统的施压？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是出于作战安排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 这样不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,进入伊萨尼尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}全员 我们即将进入Capital特区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伊赛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也在监控高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,长官阁下出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说她看起来很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没穿成这样出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你个秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁其实 是被领养的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？这么说他是养子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,具体我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,危险 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别吓唬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快回姐姐这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,长途电话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,话费可贵了 你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是 这些不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最长不许超过20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 这里总共十一只对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全买走行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,价钱好商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那边池塘里的鱼也是卖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,稍…稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿计算器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！啾啾咪不能吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,姬兰小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}姬兰小姐 你是护士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}应该更理解拉莱雅才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我家贝鲁利和艾达·苏尔坎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长 让船开稳一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,地面上的米诺夫斯基飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可比在宇宙里当海盗难多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真的打算在这里做弹射实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要能在各种环境下出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无人状态下弹射能用自动驾驶返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被撒了米诺夫斯基粒子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会像断了线的风筝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么摇晃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,低速航行容易受风影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙战舰之类 原本是把人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是把人类推向灭亡的技术象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这条航线真的能突破Capital军的警戒线？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才电话里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经让Capital卫队赶来接应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,应该可以避开军队耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要船员瞭望时做好战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔的运营长官也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是南边的伊萨尼尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是敌人领地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么敌人和敌人领地！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的故乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 非常抱歉 诺蕾朵·纳古小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 多…多谢你直言不讳的 问…问候方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,受宠若惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,受宠若惊 受宠若惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}打开格纳库 注意强风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 Montero和Gehennam可以弹射了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么 哈朋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想让那架无人的Gehennam出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,调查部的昆珀·卢西达上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他应该对荷米斯玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那是安赫尔瀑布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:51.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}安赫尔瀑布：又名天使瀑布（Angel Falls），委内瑞拉与圭亚那高原密林深处的世界最高瀑布。\N{\alpha&HFF&}安赫尔瀑布：{\alpha}1937年美国探险家詹姆斯·安赫尔对其进行考察时坠机身亡，为纪念他命名。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这样的附近有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这也叫瀑布 真让人笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏这些平顶山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,才能躲过Capital塔的雷达监视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在正规军驾驶员面前班门弄斧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,动作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是正规军驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以！史堤厄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在加速会被雷达发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,遵…遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,被撒了米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是些好战份子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史堤厄 把他们甩得远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,变形了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那够不成伤害 又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁…我这人真没用！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是上次的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 机动堡垒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不想在这里不期而遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢从绝望中拯救我 G-Self！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾达小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,开始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam别出动 败家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,开始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero的敌我识别
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让摄像机来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能用标枪 这可是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,准备 走起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,又是它！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无人驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这会让你露出破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大势已去么 芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,援军？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== Part B ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看见人让我怎么下得了手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,视野…看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,滑过了 回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,点刹车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,刹车！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,马上返回Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍作忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让我冷静一下再进舱内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,优先向昆珀上校请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,逃离Megafauna！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神 就当到了Capital塔脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,机动战士保持战斗戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,米诺夫斯基粒子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,正在消散 所以让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry-Schop也保持战备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self的技术真烂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别把甲板踩出坑来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？贝鲁这么菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是打仗累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能够顺利抵达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也归功于长官的作战计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…因为Capital卫队和军队性格不合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么 卢安先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请问长官在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是凯尔贝斯·悠教官阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 贝鲁利·赛纳姆同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是跳级生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这情况看来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是夺回了G-Self的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,凯尔贝斯 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你认得出刚才袭击这艘船的F-Rag吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital军的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了 但在下不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,贝鲁利学员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当上亚美利亚军的驾驶员了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亚美利亚军不肯给我中尉军衔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还是Capital卫队的学员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那位如果我没记错的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是海盗小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢您的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,长官亲自来电 当然得来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我还带了点伪装 帮这艘船躲避探测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟住前方的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？你跟谁说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那么长官…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital卫队的职员都像他那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,更准确地说 是宇宙脐带教的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个宇宙脐带教…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这么小？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,跟数字给人的印象完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能控制姿态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,开始测量 伊赛拉也来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收起翅片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fin put back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,测算距离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,悬停下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}5 4…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过顶梁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 看准时机着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好 关闭悬停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,躲进哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里不都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凯尔贝斯 见到长官了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们先把全新的光子电池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和压缩空气水球运来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是大四叶草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,来住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,家？住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那些货车是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,配给全世界的光子电池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全部由那些货车运往空港
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦电池上了货车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈的工作就算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,直接飞过去不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Rag不可以接近大四叶草上空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军的人可从不遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital军更像某种暴力自卫团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有经过我的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用得惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}别骑在Shank上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}来吧 来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}来吧 别只知道工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是富足带来的后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔的勤务工作十分辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每周一次的放松是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艾达·苏尔坎小姐的ID卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈·苏尔坎先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有劳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,周末没有监视？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,上校！我可以叫男友来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,说过请便！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,让面具先去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我想安排面具与茹甘司令见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 要等过完周末？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么Capital军！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人还真配得上被归入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以任其灭绝的动物种群！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧 听闻长官外出公干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚返回吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是 惊闻宇宙中祸事将至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,特来请教法皇陛下实情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？是诺蕾朵·纳古小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是否安好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 托法皇大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那便好 愿长此以往平平安安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔不会受到任何人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲想知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是否会有来自宇宙的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,纵观R.C世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:37.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an7}R.C世纪：Regild Century（重镀世纪）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,正因宇宙脐带教慈悲为怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔才得以运转至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 宇宙脐带教的教义中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,并未提及Capital塔与宇宙人的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每天清晨醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都必须从说明空气的成分开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,难道阁下认为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光子电池是太空中自然形成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,无法对光子电池进行分解或维修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,强行为之 会导致爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才被归入禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才助长了恶意垄断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们亚美利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为从Capital塔的垄断中解放地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这种想法才是最大的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,韦米特·赛纳姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到长官已经凯旋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,昆珀上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,您周末的休假呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,苏尔坎总监为什么也在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想请教昆珀上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,关于荷米斯玫瑰设计图的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您知情吗
